"pid":"660ed75dc2d16958040e83d2be8a8b866d9afc9b","tid":1849054,"uid":283207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d535e510bd91519259c0164a6d9acfe885bcf72e","tid":1849054,"uid":37803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1dd46804ae319f9452627d04b66f06ab087c0a9a","tid":1849054,"uid":283207,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e9ae8bc1e1d7d4cb4f114a78820933ce09bd721a","tid":1849054,"uid":93984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T02:35:28.000Z","msg":"巴打意思係希臘?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T03:30:53.000Z","msg":"克羅地亞同黑山都好正，消費又平d"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T12:38:12.000Z","msg":"小弟第一次獨遊去羅馬尼亞，第二次就去黑山+阿爾巴尼亞+科索沃+馬其頓"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T12:55:55.000Z","msg":"有冇第2次旅程分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec109f6466e4d4496eb414f536ff353f19869180","tid":1849054,"uid":37803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"660ed75dc2d16958040e83d2be8a8b866d9afc9b","tid":1849054,"uid":283207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d535e510bd91519259c0164a6d9acfe885bcf72e","tid":1849054,"uid":37803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1dd46804ae319f9452627d04b66f06ab087c0a9a","tid":1849054,"uid":283207,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T03:30:53.000Z","msg":"克羅地亞同黑山都好正，消費又平d"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T12:38:12.000Z","msg":"小弟第一次獨遊去羅馬尼亞，第二次就去黑山+阿爾巴尼亞+科索沃+馬其頓"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T12:55:55.000Z","msg":"有冇第2次旅程分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T15:04:28.000Z","msg":"可以share下我個行程，好似去左15日左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黑山：喺倫敦飛黑山，玩budva同kotor。kotor個城牆如果上到頂都要一段時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n克羅地亞dubrovnik：kotor大巴去dubrovnik。個人覺得overrated同埋使費係全程最貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n波斯尼亞trebinje ：dubrovnik小巴去trebinje。除咗有個仿照科索沃gracanica monestery嘅修道院之外冇咩特別嘅小鎮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，之後巴士返kotor。<br />\n<br />\n阿爾巴尼亞tirana：kotor大巴去tirana。Tirana 近幾年大興土木，d建築好色彩鮮艷。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />阿爾巴尼亞人非常之熱情，英文都好好。佢個碉堡博物館可以睇到點解呢個國家咁多碉堡。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n阿爾巴尼亞berat: tirana 巴士去berat。berat 叫做千窗之城，因為佢河邊d樓全部都好密好多窗。佢個古城都值得睇睇。<br />\n<br />\n馬其頓ohrid: berat 巴士去elbasan，的士去阿邊境，再轉的士去ohrid。一個好似仙境嘅湖，甚至可以話係我個trip嘅highlight<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />stay咗3日睇佢湖邊，撐艇睇日落等等<br />\n<br />\n馬其頓skopje: 一個好誇張，好多雕塑嘅首都。<br />\n<br />\n科索沃prizren：科索沃以阿爾巴尼亞人為主，所以都非常之熱情，prizren城牆同河邊嘅日落都係好出名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n科索沃pristina：我特登喺佢國慶日去，感受到科索沃人對美帝嘅尊敬。<br />\n<br />\n之後碌返落skopje再落希臘thessaloniki 同athens飛返英國"},{"pid":"14afd545c93c4919fbb6b5767f8e1eac186fd279","tid":1849054,"uid":283207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T15:59:25.000Z","msg":"估唔到馬其頓其中一個地方咁吸引<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有機會下次都會去你呢條路線。<br />\n我上次係去哂成個 Croatia，由 Zagreb 去左Rovinj 個邊再慢慢掃返落中間zadar十六湖等等最後都有去Dubrovnik，認同你講既係，呢個城市太商業化，洗費貴到離譜相比其他城市之下，GOT fans去就唔錯既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋太多樓梯，老啦真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5d05d06481715aa89fce6890f8b97c9481857fe","tid":1849054,"uid":194120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:38:40.000Z","msg":"平平地去東歐，匈牙利捷克波蘭，或者波羅的海三國。"},{"pid":"9a49e88572f4cea5f571410c6b4959aabf70153f","tid":1849054,"uid":37803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14afd545c93c4919fbb6b5767f8e1eac186fd279","tid":1849054,"uid":283207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T15:59:25.000Z","msg":"估唔到馬其頓其中一個地方咁吸引<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有機會下次都會去你呢條路線。<br />\n我上次係去哂成個 Croatia，由 Zagreb 去左Rovinj 個邊再慢慢掃返落中間zadar十六湖等等最後都有去Dubrovnik，認同你講既係，呢個城市太商業化，洗費貴到離譜相比其他城市之下，GOT fans去就唔錯既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋太多樓梯，老啦真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T21:35:32.000Z","msg":"其實克羅地亞都有d相對小人d嘅地方可以chill下，例如zadar聽下海風琴，或者hvar出發睇藍洞等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> split同dubrovnik就不了"},{"pid":"ed729738c4244823f31873f88f1b2ef0a7c4b036","tid":1849054,"uid":49044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec109f6466e4d4496eb414f536ff353f19869180","tid":1849054,"uid":37803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"660ed75dc2d16958040e83d2be8a8b866d9afc9b","tid":1849054,"uid":283207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d535e510bd91519259c0164a6d9acfe885bcf72e","tid":1849054,"uid":37803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T12:38:12.000Z","msg":"小弟第一次獨遊去羅馬尼亞，第二次就去黑山+阿爾巴尼亞+科索沃+馬其頓"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T12:55:55.000Z","msg":"有冇第2次旅程分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T15:04:28.000Z","msg":"可以share下我個行程，好似去左15日左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黑山：喺倫敦飛黑山，玩budva同kotor。kotor個城牆如果上到頂都要一段時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><